383
00:24:50,484 --> 00:24:52,691
Hey, Park Sung Soo!

384
00:24:53,826 --> 00:24:56,612
- You really came.
- It's been so long.

385
00:24:57,200 --> 00:24:58,951
Have you been well?
How's your mom doing?

386
00:24:58,951 --> 00:25:01,000
Thanks to you,
she's gotten a lot healthier.

387
00:25:01,750 --> 00:25:04,217
- I'm not late, am I?
- Not at all.

388
00:25:04,217 --> 00:25:08,530
